headline: Intercontinental Exchange Announces Results from 2025 Annual Meeting of Stockholders
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, May 20, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced the results of the Company’s 2025 Annual Meeting of Stockholders, which was held Friday, May 16. A replay of the meeting is available at www.ir.theice.com.
